   <text>
      <body divRole="original-translation">
         <div type="original" xml:lang="nl">
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.1" f="1r" facs="#s1r" n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.1" n="1">Vrijdag<ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.1"/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.2" n="2">B.J.,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.3" n="3">Ik heb een paar dingen gemaakt met de <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#127">Vincent</rs> op de achtergrond.<ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.2"/> Als je ze misschien wilt komen zien, kom dan morgennamiddag (blijf dan eten), want Zaterdag gaan er een paar <pb f="1v" facs="#s1v" n="2"/> naar Buffa. <ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.3"/> Ik moet wel morgenmiddag om half 5 een bezoek brengen maar wat <hi rend="italics">mij</hi> aangaat komt dat er niet op aan.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.4" n="4" rend="indent">Ik wacht je dan morgen.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.5" n="5">Vele groeten</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.6" n="6">I.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.7" n="7">Kom zoo vroeg je wilt, bv. bij de koffie, al heb ik ’s middags dan nog wat te doen.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.3" f="2r" facs="#2r3" n="3"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.8" n="8">Mevr. J. Cohen Gosschalk</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.9" n="9">Koninginneweg 77</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.10" n="10">Amsterdam</p>
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.4" f="2v" facs="#2v4" n="4"/>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.1"
                corresp="#pb.orig.nl.1"
                f="1r"
                facs="#s1r"
                n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.1"
               corresp="#p.orig.nl.1"
               style="text-align: left; "
               n="1">Friday<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.1"/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.2"
               corresp="#p.orig.nl.2"
               style="text-align: left; "
               n="2">Dear J.,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.3"
               corresp="#p.orig.nl.3"
               style="text-align: left; "
               n="3">I’ve made a few things with the <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#127">Vincent</rs> in the background.<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.2"/> If you’d like to come and see them, come tomorrow afternoon (then stay and eat), because a couple of them are going <pb f="1v" facs="#s1v" n="2"/> to Buffa on Saturday.<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.3"/> I have to pay a visit at half past 4 tomorrow afternoon, but as far as <hi rend="italics">I</hi> am concerned it doesn’t matter.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.4"
               corresp="#p.orig.nl.4"
               style="text-align: left; "
               n="4"
               rend="indent">I’ll expect you tomorrow.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.5"
               corresp="#p.orig.nl.5"
               style="text-align: left; "
               n="5">Best wishes</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.6"
               corresp="#p.orig.nl.6"
               style="text-align: left; "
               n="6">I.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.7"
               corresp="#p.orig.nl.7"
               style="text-align: left; "
               n="7">Come as early as you like, at coffee time for instance, although I do still have things to do in the afternoon.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.3"
                corresp="#pb.orig.nl.3"
                f="2r"
                facs="#2r3"
                n="3"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.8"
               corresp="#p.orig.nl.8"
               style="text-align: left; "
               n="8">Mevr. J. Cohen Gosschalk</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.9"
               corresp="#p.orig.nl.9"
               style="text-align: left; "
               n="9">Koninginneweg 77</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.10"
               corresp="#p.orig.nl.10"
               style="text-align: left; "
               n="10">Amsterdam</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.4"
                corresp="#pb.orig.nl.4"
                f="2v"
                facs="#2v4"
                n="4"/>
         </div>
      </body>
